Girls Are Awesome x Wmns Forum Low 'White Purple Beauty'
results.story: The Girls Are Awesome x adidas women’s Forum Low ‘White Purple Beauty’ is drawn from a larger collection made in partnership with the Copenhagen-based agency dedicated to gender equality. The retro low-top makes use of an off-white leather upper with contrasting purple and gold accents. Girls Are Awesome branding is embroidered on a chenille midfoot overlay. The fuzzy fabric is repeated on detachable ankle straps inscribed with the names of various international cities, including Paris, New York, London and Tokyo.

Wmns RS-Curve 'Sunset'
results.story: The PUMA women’s RS-Curve ‘Sunset’ pairs flowing lines with warm hues that evoke the golden hour. The upper is constructed from peach-colored mesh with contrasting overlays in black and lavender. Purple webbing pull tabs are decorated with PUMA’s jumping cag logo in yellow, matching the leather Formstrip stitched onto the side panel. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a sculpted polyurethane midsole, supported underfoot by a grippy gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns UltraBoost 21 'White Hazy Rose'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 21 ‘White Hazy Rose’ highlights subtle pops of color on a performance runner designed for enhanced energy return. A stark white finish distinguishes a Primeknit upper that incorporates Primeblue, a high-performance material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. A translucent heel counter in a contrasting dark pink hue provides rearfoot support. The sneaker is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, designed to yield a more responsive ride with the addition of a revised Torsion system dubbed Linear Energy Push.

Wmns UltraBoost 21 'Hazy Rose'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 21 ‘Hazy Rose’ showcases a monochromatic finish throughout the exterior of the running shoe. The lightweight Primeknit upper, featuring recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester, sits atop a full-length Boost midsole with 6% more Boost capsules than previous UltraBoost models. A revised Torsion system, dubbed Linear Energy Push, provides less flex in the forefoot for a more responsive ride.

Wmns React Escape Run 'Vast Grey Pink Glaze'
results.story: Built on a last developed specifically for the female foot, the Nike women’s React Escape Run ‘Vast Grey Pink Glaze’ pairs pastel accents with an otherwise neutral color scheme. A subtle grey finish floods the minimalist mesh upper, featuring semi-translucent midfoot paneling and a wider collar that accommodates the forward placement of the female ankle. Plush cushioning is provided by a stacked Nike React midsole, bolstered underfoot by a grippy gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Hedra 'Dark Dreams - Black'
results.story: Launching as part of the ‘Dark Dreams’ collection, the PUMA women’s Hedra ‘Black’ features a ripstop nylon upper with tonal suede overlays at the toe and heel. A patent leather Formstrip in matching black adorns each of the side panels. A decorative gold chain is draped around the back of the collar, complementing the sneaker’s eyelets and a PUMA logo plate affixed to the heel of the IMEVA midsole. Underfoot, the rubber outsole wraps up the sidewalls for enhanced traction and durability.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Agravic TR 'Hazy Emerald'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Agravic TR 'Hazy Emerald' highlights pastel tones on a rugged low-top built for outdoor adventures. Breathable mesh construction on the upper is fortified with synthetic abrasion-resistant overlays in bright teal finish. An integrated lacing system delivers midfoot lockdown, while an external heel counter in Hazy Orange provides rearfoot stability. The same hue is repeated on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported by a lugged Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Metcon 6 'Football Grey Arctic Punch'
results.story: The Nike women’s Metcon 6 ‘Football Grey Arctic Punch’ uses a delicate pink hue as a display of fortitude. The pastel finish is applied to the training shoe’s rubber outsole, featuring a wide, stable platform and extended coverage that wraps up the sneaker’s sidewalls, a signature attribute of the Metcon line. The upper is built with a lightweight mesh forefoot, reinforced with a durable screen print and offering 18% more breathability than the Metcon 5.

results.name: Wmns Hedra 'Dark Dreams - Nimbus Cloud'
results.story: Taken from the ‘Dark Dreams’ collection, the PUMA women’s Hedra ‘Nimbus Cloud’ showcases a ripstop, leather and suede build, rendered in neutral white and off-white tones. A patent leather Formstrip and subtle pastel accents are overshadowed by gilded detailing, including stitched eyelets, a gold chain looped around the back of the collar and a PUMA logo plate affixed to the rear of the IMEVA midsole. Its sidewalls are partially wrapped up by the sneaker’s high-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: Takahashi Hiroko x Wmns Adilette Shower Slide 'Black White'
results.story: Designed in partnership with the Japanese textile artist, the Takahashi Hiroko x adidas women’s Adilette Shower Slide ‘Black White’ updates the versatile slip-on with a glossy patent-leather bandage strap, decorated with the brand’s signature three-stripes and lined in soft textile for a comfortable fit. The lightweight and durable EVA midsole is layered up top with a plush Cloudfoam footbed. Underfoot, a herringbone-traction outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: Wmns Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX 'Core Black'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Skychaser XT Mid GTX ‘Core Black’ packs a responsive ride, thanks to the combination of a molded sockliner and full-length Boost midsole, partially encaged with a Promoderator plate for increased stability. Underfoot, a lugged Continental rubber outsole provides sure footing on uneven terrain. The mid-top carries a breathable black mesh upper, secured with a drawcord lacing system and reinforced with a waterproof Gore-Tex membrane. An EVA stabilization frame provides lightweight durability and support.

results.name: Wmns Future Rider 'Dark Dreams'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Future Rider 'Dark Dreams' treats the lifestyle runner to a sleek, fashion-forward makeover. A monochromatic black finish is applied to the upper, constructed from nylon ripstop with suede overlays and patent leather detailing on the heel tab and signature Formstrip. The blacked-out aesthetic is disrupted by PUMA branding hits at the tongue and heel, as well as a metallic gold chain attached to the lateral eyestay. The sneaker rides on an EVA midsole, supported underfoot by PUMA’s Federbein outsole in a neon yellow hue.

results.name: Wmns Kyron 'Dark Dreams'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Kyron ‘Dark Dreams’ blends the German brand’s running heritage with detailing borrowed from the world of high fashion. Partially concealed laces secure a black ripstop upper with tonal synthetic leather overlays. Contrasting blue lines distinguish the patent leather Formstrip, while metallic gold trim atop the toe box is matched by a gold chain attached to the back heel. The rubber outsole wraps up and over the forefoot of the EVA midsole for added traction and durability.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform Low 'My Story'
Nike Air Max Up City Special NYC (W)
results.story: Releasing as part of the ‘City Special’ collection, the Nike women’s Air Max Up ‘NYC Lady Liberty’ honors the Big Apple with a bright green finish intended to evoke the Statue of Liberty’s oxidized copper exterior. Ripstop textile is utilized on the upper, featuring tonal no-sew overlays and partially concealed laces for a sleek aesthetic. ‘NYC’ is stamped on gold lace jewels and inscribed on a small woven tag on the lateral collar. The sneaker sits on a stacked foam midsole, enhanced with a large-volume Max Air unit housed within a TPU frame.

results.name: Wmns Free RN 5.0 By You
results.story: Designed via the brand’s customization platform, the Nike women’s Free RN 5.0 By You is built on a firm foam sole unit that uses deep cuts to deliver flexible cushioning and a natural stride. The seamless bootie-style upper is secured with off-center lacing for an optimal fit. No-sew overlays provide lightweight support and durability, while three foam pods are built into the interior heel that makes the back of the foot feel more comfortable and locked in.

Wmns Waffle Racer Crater 'Pale Ivory Electric Green'
results.story: The Nike women’s Waffle Racer Crater ‘Pale Ivory Electric Green’ reinvents the vintage 1977 runner with refreshed details and a sustainable build. Semi-concealed laces secure recycled textile twill upper, finished in a subtle ivory hue and reinforced with grey suede overlays at the toe and heel. Neon green zigzag stitching surrounds the black leather Swoosh, matching the Nike branded leather heel tab. The sneaker rides on a Crater Foam midsole, supported by a classic waffle tread outsole made in part with Nike Grind.

results.name: Wmns React Infinity Run Flyknit 2 'Sunset Pulse'
Nike Dunk High Sail Football Grey (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk High ‘Football Grey’ delivers an understated colorway of the retro hoops shoe originally released in 1985, featuring an outsole borrowed from the Air Jordan 1 and an upper design redolent of both the Air Jordan 1 and Nike Terminator. Here, the leather upper makes use of an off-white base with contrasting overlays in a subtle pale blue finish. A padded mesh collar combines with a nylon tongue to deliver a comfortable fit.

results.name: Wmns Zoom Air Fire 'White Dark Beetroot'
results.story: The Nike women’s Zoom Air Fire 'White Dark Beetroot' combines plush cushioning with design cues borrowed from classic runners of the past. The upper is constructed from breathable white mesh with tonal synthetic overlays throughout. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a stacked foam midsole, housing a visible Zoom Air unit in the heel surrounded by a burgundy-colored TPU frame — a unique detail that recalls the tooling of the Air Zoom Spiridon Cage 2.
